name: r-qqplotr
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.0.4" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-qqplotr
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/qqplotr_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/qqplotr/qqplotr_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 73680feb312468ce3863b725836a2640b5123712ac6845457636024a2dadc7ff

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-dplyr
    - r-ggplot2 >=2.2
    - r-knitr
    - r-purrr
    - r-rmarkdown
    - r-robustbase
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-dplyr
    - r-ggplot2 >=2.2
    - r-knitr
    - r-purrr
    - r-rmarkdown
    - r-robustbase

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('qqplotr')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('qqplotr')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/aloy/qqplotr
  license: GPL-3
  summary: Extensions of 'ggplot2' Q-Q plot functionalities.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
